OPDUMPER
--------
opdumper - A tiny and simple php extension that dumps opcodes of PHP script.

VERSION
-------
version: 0.0.1

SUPPORT
-------
PHP 5.3 / PHP 5.4 support

INSTALL
-------
	phpize
	./configure
	make & make install

DUMP OPCODE
-----------
* dump opcodes
	php -dopdumer.active=1 foo.php
* dump opcodes and keep raw code
	php -dopdumer.active=1 -dopdumer.raw=1 foo.php
